1
00:00:02,202 --> 00:00:06,879
Opening its first store,
OLIVE YOUNG has officially entered the US market,

2
00:00:06,880 --> 00:00:10,143
the world’s leading beauty trendsetter.

3
00:00:10,143 --> 00:00:12,925
To mark the beginning
of this exciting new chapter,

4
00:00:12,926 --> 00:00:17,985
Chairman Lee Jay Hyun visited
OLIVE YOUNG Pasadena to meet with the team.

5
00:00:25,592 --> 00:00:29,204
Driven by OLIVE YOUNG’s DNA
of relentless innovation,

6
00:00:29,205 --> 00:00:31,577
the mission to share the value of healthy beauty

7
00:00:31,578 --> 00:00:35,669
beyond Korea and into the global market
has now begun.

8
00:00:42,009 --> 00:00:45,408
In May 2026, OLIVE YOUNG’s global journey

9
00:00:45,409 --> 00:00:47,981
reached a new milestone in the United States.

10
00:00:56,456 --> 00:01:00,148
The opening of OLIVE YOUNG’s
first US store in Pasadena

11
00:01:00,149 --> 00:01:03,035
marks its first step
into the American beauty market

12
00:01:03,036 --> 00:01:06,733
and the beginning of a new mission to go global.

13
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:43,353
As a differentiated
beauty and lifestyle platform,

14
00:01:43,354 --> 00:01:47,850
OLIVE YOUNG offers a completely new
beauty experience to customers in the US,

15
00:01:47,851 --> 00:01:51,336
one that sets it apart from competing retailers.

16
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:10,685
From an expanded curated selection
spanning beauty to lifestyle products

17
00:02:10,686 --> 00:02:12,959
to expert health and beauty routine know-how

18
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:16,037
and its signature
friendly and dynamic customer service,

19
00:02:16,038 --> 00:02:21,041
OLIVE YOUNG offers a never-before-seen
comprehensive customer experience.

20
00:03:15,028 --> 00:03:17,427
OLIVE YOUNG has only just taken the first step.

21
00:03:17,428 --> 00:03:21,253
The expansion of its US operations,
both online and offline,

22
00:03:21,254 --> 00:03:22,870
is expected to accelerate.

23
00:03:22,870 --> 00:03:26,791
OLIVE YOUNG plans to build
its core presence in the West

24
00:03:26,792 --> 00:03:28,609
with California as the hub,

25
00:03:28,609 --> 00:03:33,780
and then gradually expand
to East and South-Central US.

26
00:03:57,604 --> 00:04:01,429
Customers had looked forward
to OLIVE YOUNG’s opening so much

27
00:04:01,430 --> 00:04:03,716
that a long line stretched outside.

28
00:04:03,717 --> 00:04:06,263
And the Pasadena store is already providing them

29
00:04:06,264 --> 00:04:09,650
with a new experience unique to OLIVE YOUNG.

30
00:04:09,650 --> 00:04:11,836
During his visit to OLIVE YOUNG Pasadena,

31
00:04:11,837 --> 00:04:15,236
Chairman Lee Jay Hyun offered the staff
words of encouragement

32
00:04:15,237 --> 00:04:17,991
for taking the first steps
onto the global stage.

33
00:04:43,851 --> 00:04:46,984
He stressed that the opening
of OLIVE YOUNG Pasadena

34
00:04:46,985 --> 00:04:50,237
marks a great beginning of a quest
to the global stage.

35
00:04:50,238 --> 00:04:53,947
He urged the staff to go beyond
K-beauty and K-wellness

36
00:04:53,948 --> 00:05:00,534
and encourage US customers to embrace
a healthy, stylish everyday lifestyle.

37
00:05:26,593 --> 00:05:32,285
OLIVE YOUNG’s new mission of bringing
true K-beauty and K-lifestyle to the US market

38
00:05:32,286 --> 00:05:34,168
has already begun.

39
00:05:34,701 --> 00:05:39,806
And this journey is now set to accelerate
across the global stage.

